<div class="terms-condition-area pt-100 pb-70">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="condition-content pr-20">
                    <h2 class="mb-4">Affiliation</h2>

                    <p>
                        <strong>Sree Muthukumaraswamy College</strong> is affiliated with a reputed and recognized university, ensuring that our academic programs meet the highest educational standards prescribed by the Government and University authorities. This affiliation enables our institution to provide degree programs that are current, relevant, and aligned with industry needs.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        The college strictly adheres to the curriculum, examination systems, and quality benchmarks outlined by the affiliating university. Our faculty actively participate in university-level academic activities, workshops, and committees, contributing to the continuous improvement of higher education standards.
                    </p>

                    <h2 class="mt-5 mb-4">Accreditation</h2>

                    <p>
                        <strong>Sree Muthukumaraswamy College</strong> is recognized by the <strong>University Grants Commission (UGC)</strong> under Sections 2(f) and 12(B) of the UGC Act, which enables the institution to receive developmental assistance and participate in national-level educational initiatives.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        The institution has also undergone assessment by the <strong>National Assessment and Accreditation Council (NAAC)</strong>, which evaluates higher education institutions on various parameters such as curriculum, teaching-learning processes, research, infrastructure, student support, and governance.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Through these accreditations and affiliations, we continuously strive to maintain and enhance the standards of education, transparency, and accountability across all institutional activities.
                    </p>

                    <h4 class="mt-5">Commitment to Quality</h4>
                    <p>
                        We are committed to achieving excellence in higher education through continuous improvement, quality assurance practices, and a strong sense of responsibility toward our students and the community. Our institutional policies reflect our dedication to holistic growth and sustainable development.
                    </p>

                    <div class="text-center mt-5">
                        <img src="~/img/accreditation/affiliation.jpg" alt="Accreditation and Affiliation" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm" style="max-width:600px;">
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
